{{Quote|Our unit was trapped at the Tylerin Embankment, and instead of performing her duty she went right by our position and surrendered her weapons, her craft and herself to the Impies!|[[Lieutenant/Legends|Lieutenant]] [[Akul Witig]], about [[Mosara Thiirn]]|<ref name="Alliance Intelligence Reports">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref>}}
'''Tylerin Embankment''' was a location near the eastern seas of the planet [[Archais]] During the [[Battle of Archais]], [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] [[Lieutenant/Legends|lieutenant]] [[Akul Witig]]'s unit (probably [[Midnight Squadron]] or [[Storm Squadron (Rebel)|Storm Squadron]]) was trapped in the Tylerin Enbankment when Rebel [[Officer/Legends|officer]] [[Mosara Thiirn]] surrender [[Gender/Legends|her]] ship and herself to the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] forces. Due to this, Witig's unit was on increased danger and they only survived thanks to the patchwork of fellow Rebel [[Shaparo]] and some maneuvers of [[Norrion Glidamir]] &mdash; but they still held a great grudge towards Thiirn, because due to her many good men died that day.

